      "## The Note Families That Read as Luxury",
      "Luxury, in scent terms, lives mostly in the base — the heavy, slow-evaporating notes that linger longest and give a fragrance its sense of depth. These are the materials that have anchored fine perfumery for centuries. Each has a distinct character, and each pairs naturally with certain companions.",
